    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and <strong>peeled garlic </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>(use <strong>tin foil </strong>to avoid mess!) and cook for 15-20 min or until softened and starting to brown – this is your <strong>roasted pepper & garlic</strong></p><p>Once softened, remove from the oven and set aside to cool</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
