    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>ground cumin </strong>and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) on a plate with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>Cajun-style seasoning</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in half lengthways and pat them dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Press the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>basa </strong>into the <strong>Cajun-style seasoning</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>Cajun-style basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
