    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>shallot[s] </strong>and chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Strip your<strong> mint leaves </strong>from their stems and chop them finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the<strong> diced</strong> <strong>tomato </strong>and <strong>diced shallot </strong>in a bowl with your<strong> rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped mint leaves </strong>and<strong> chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and set aside – this is your <strong>salsa</strong></p>",
